{"tid":433351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"粵語/香港語必須盡早「去中國化」","createTime":"2017-10-12T10:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T04:25:31.000Z","uid":13173,"like":138,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"b7ed0e184428d0287f34f22b0d9b9ff25f32a539","tid":433351,"uid":13173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:16:30.000Z","msg":"要避免日後獨有粵語用法/文法消失，香港人實在要盡早建立切合香港粵語用字嘅獨立書寫系統，先至可以更清楚咁分辨出香港粵語同其他基於漢字嘅語言。否則，會畀「現代漢語」入侵，最後同化成所謂「中文」。<br />\n<br />\n而最首要第一步就係要停止繼續稱呼「粵語」做「中文」。"},{"pid":"cd849a3f7fbc95bfc82383f232e5a29004502f3e","tid":433351,"uid":51129,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:17:43.000Z","msg":"「去xx化」呢啲係叫咩化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760a17f8abc16956d1e910aec149393fe2bb3e48","tid":433351,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:46:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「去xx化」呢啲係叫咩化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英文硬譯"},{"pid":"2ee1c836a9a6809ab1bd76fd1fc10c7d7c54029d","tid":433351,"uid":79563,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:53:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>「去xx化」呢啲係叫咩化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英文硬譯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nde-chinalization"},{"pid":"efcaafb14f8b9c8ee4d5ac762d9feff689577914","tid":433351,"uid":128229,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:54:20.000Z","msg":"但用既文字都係中文啵"},{"pid":"681f0dac44f45e7bf34a094a9e6a4ac46a07f852","tid":433351,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:54:52.000Z","msg":"「中國」二字個概念本身就好有問題<br />\n<br />\n我覺得直接唔用就好"},{"pid":"2bb7cd31fb3c93c328eb2955541fb861bc170af7","tid":433351,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:55:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但用既文字都係中文啵</blockquote><br />\n粵字"},{"pid":"f19ff0b086d