變先保持漢字 同樣地冇漢字日文一樣可以function到</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n韓國人自己都話就咁個詞未必知人地講咩<br />\n一定要成句講先知上文下理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啫係人地都舉埋例畀佢都要話冇問題<br />\n點解要咁頑固</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只不過唔用漢字既好處多過你要用漢字區分同音字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd8b1a50d75d39d4371800ecdffade142fab398","tid":433351,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:45:44.000Z","msg":"毒果日日都用支那語"},{"pid":"84f2af889564e336c4cfb0ee36af4d4f250dab46","tid":433351,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:53:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諺文化嘅意思係？<br />\n<br />\n但係有咩方法可以入區呢？因為巴打你上面個方法只限於會上網嘅年青人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個到講緊嘅「諺文化」就係根據方形字結構，但以切合粵語嘅規則去創造一套圖形文字書寫系統，類似諺文咁。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問下諗住點解決同音字問題?<br />\n日本仲保留漢字係因為解決唔到同音字嘅分別，<br />\n成功，製鋼，精工甚至性向喺佢地嘅拼音都係せいこう（Seikou），冇漢字就要全部靠估<br />\n班泡菜佬就試過因為個拼音分唔清防水同放水，搞到好撚大件事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢啲字唔係常用字 係學術上用多 現實生活根本唔會有好大影響 <span style=\"color: red;\">韓文用純諺文係冇問題  </span>反而你加埋漢字令到成個system好亂<br />\n日文唔廢係因為歷史同傳統文化因素 佢地唔想改變先保持漢字 同樣地冇漢字日文一樣可以function到</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n韓國人自己都話就咁個詞未必知人地講咩<br />\n一定要成句講先知上文下理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啫係人地都舉埋例畀佢都要話冇問題<br />\n點解要咁頑固</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只不過唔用漢字既好處多過你要用漢字區分同音字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n取中庸之道，個同音字會影響到理解就用漢字，唔影響就拉丁"},{"pid":"6ca1cd0a28cf0a10d3cf101344263422f416e49f","tid":433351,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:58:26.000Z","msg":"btw,我曾經講過粵文要拉丁化但畀人狂插話行唔通"},{"pid":"6c5720a9257195e046fbc15d9fb684a050d9a9ea","tid":433351,"uid":13257,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T15:00:33.000Z","msg":"淨係睇下陳雲本中文解毒，你會發覺而家d中文係毒到爛"},{"pid":"3b6847106b8c57bd58706951d04b29a842db61a2","tid":433351,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T15:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013d1495d19df37b216fd51df442c838ba8ac425","tid":433351,"uid":99225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T15:51:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw,我曾經講過粵文要拉丁化但畀人狂插話行唔通</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一定行得通 只不過啲傳統觀念太重"},{"pid":"ff1148d223e2d05a50159dcb272cf0d19780e208","tid":433351,"uid":55689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:03:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但用既文字都係中文啵</blockquote><br />\n粵字</blockquote><br />\n首先，要搞清楚中國語文/官話文 同漢字個概念係咩先。好多人將中國語文/官話文同漢字掛勾咗。其實中國語文/官話文同好多外文一樣，譬如越南文、馬來文、日文可以用羅馬拼音表示唔一定用到漢字。使用漢字嘅國家或者地區亦都未必都用所謂中文...."},{"pid":"49734a0a604e5806579792f6defbbdc4c1366969","tid":433351,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T17:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1b3e275ac78de55b751d14202e9b8d52025d0d","tid":433351,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T17:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04151b488328ac9b5338925038001cf2d0858ff9","tid":433351,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T17:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gi